samtools (used  version: 0.1.18 (r982:295))
R (used version: 2.15.0)
Python 2.7 (used version:  r27:82500, Aug 07 2010, 16:54:59)
Perl (used version: v5.12.3)
BioPerl (used version: 1.58)

